FTX held a diluted 7.84% stake in Anthropic, according to Reuters.<p>Anthropic’s latest reported valuation is around $965B.<p>That implies the former FTX stake would be worth about $75B before further dilution.<p>FTX’s customer shortfall was roughly $8B to $9B.<p>The estate sold the Anthropic stake during bankruptcy to repay creditors.<p>Sources:
